{% doc %}
  @prompt
    I have just 3 main categories in my shop I would like some kind of animated section to show up this 3 main categories as a clickeable element, remove the title section and the shop now button, and just make it appear once you hover it, I need to be able to fix the padding of the section, to add a heading, sub heading, body text and a see all products button, I would like to make the images to overflow outside the card container on the top side of it, please include a way to adjust the amount of overflow, Move the see all products under/after the cards, I want to be able to set an image as background, I want to be able to change the background color or set an image as background for the section

{% enddoc %}
